Paul Abdul, 60, has taken to Instagram in stunning snaps as the Straight Up hitmaker showed off a new outfit. The post was shared with her 474,000 followers.  She was strutting in a carefree manner on a driveway as the star mimicked a catwalk.  Paula was dressed in a chic all-white suit, with a yellow shirt and a flower buttoned to her lapel.  The star stunned with her brunette hair worn in bangs and a ponytail.  Famous fans such as Paris Hilton and Nicole Scherzinger took to the comments in support of her.  Nicole wrote: “Omg you’re everything,” while Paris commented with a love heart eye emoji.